
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-mip4-dynamic-assignment-07.txt'>
    <title>"Mobile IPv4 Dynamic Home Agent Assignment", Miland Kulkarni</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-mip4-dynamic-assignment-07.txt</link>
    <description>Mobile IPv4 [1] uses the Home Agent (HA) to anchor sessions of a roaming Mobile Node (MN). This draft proposes a messaging mechanism for dynamic home agent assignment and HA redirection. The goal is to provide a mechanism to assign an optimal HA for a Mobile IP session while allowing any suitable method for HA selection.</description>
    <dc:date>2005-12-15T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
